      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior has minor surface scratches and small rock chips on the hood. The interior shows light wear on the driver's seat and steering wheel. All mechanical and electronic systems are functioning as intended.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing dependable transportation on a budget. The engine and transmission are in good working order, ensuring the car is fully drivable and safe for the road. However, potential buyers should expect some visible wear and tear, including minor exterior dings and some staining on the interior upholstery. It has been recently serviced to ensure mechanical soundess, making it a practical choice for a commuter car or a first vehicle.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom delivery. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade asset that satisfies even the most discerning collector. We invite you to experience a specimen that remains indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it strictly in the garage, and never missed a service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for an adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a true driver's specimen featuring the S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components to ensure valvetrain longevity. The 6-speed Getrag manual shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that provides telepathic feedback. The suspension geometry is stock and tight, utilizing fresh bushings and OEM dampers to maintain its legendary handling profile. No fluid leaks, no pixel degradation in the cluster, and original VIN tags are present on all panels. This is a turn-key collector-grade machine for the purist who demands mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Clean title.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is the definition of 'mint.' The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with professional ceramic coating and zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, featuring pristine leather that still carries that new-car scent; it has been kept completely smoke-free and pet-free. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership, with a thick folder of documentation to prove its pedigree. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot: tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. Complete with both original keys, all factory manuals, and a clean title. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning driver who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate condition, this vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence. Meticulously curated and preserved in showroom state, it offers a level of refinement and mechanical integrity that is increasingly rare. This is a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking a vehicle that defies the typical wear of time. Experience unrivaled quality in every detail.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    }
